The exercise link - https://aws-dojo.com/excercises/excercise11

EC2 Image Builder simplifies the creation, maintenance, validation, sharing, and deployment of Linux or Windows Server images for use with Amazon EC2 and on-premises. Image Builder is offered at no cost, other than the cost of the underlying AWS resources used to create, store, and share the images.
